      <div class="msgContentFrame">Hi All, <br /> <br />I am a gladiator and would like to combine it with a conjurer class.  I know I can play them individually by changing the weapon.  But I want to play a gladitor and heal myself using conjurer abilities without switching to the conjurer class.  Is this not possible? <br /> <br />My stats: <br /> <br />Gladiator: 10 <br />Miner: 10 <br />Goldsmith: 8 <br />Blksmith: 8 <br />Armor: 5</div>
