      <div class="msgContentFrame">Yes this is very possible, recommended, and useful.  When assigning your actions/traits simply scroll over to the right side of the menu and choose the class that contains the ability you wish to equip and then do so as normal.  Customize it any way you see fit.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Original Swinging of Kashuan-Limsa Lominsa <br />*Marauder-Gladiator-Goldsmith* <br />Swingingmeat of Ifrit (retired) <br />75 NIN PLD SAM 73 THF <br />Bastok Rank 10 <br />Rise of the Zilart-Complete <br />CoP-Complete</div></div>
