      <div class="msgContentFrame">When you check on an ability it's write who can use it. <br /> <br />For a War or Magic job is mostly be write &quot;Requires: Disciplines of War or Magic&quot; if so, you can equip it with every War of Magic job, but some will be X Class only like Tranquility for Conjurer it's write &quot;Requires: Conjury&quot; so only the conjury can use it. ^^<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/965232.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
